title: Counter Strike : Global Offensive [No-Steam] Warzone
description:
ABOUT THE GAME
Counter-Strike: Global Offensive (CS: GO) will expand upon the team-based action gameplay that it pioneered when it was launched 12 years ago. CS: GO features new maps, characters, and weapons and delivers updated versions of the classic CS content. In addition, CS: GO will introduce new gameplay modes, matchmaking, leader boards, and more.

FEATURES
- 100% clean rip from Steam game content
- 3.5GB highly compressed installer size
- Include build-in auto updater
- Working game inventory and items
- Working server browser with Internet, Favourite and LAN tabs
- Working offline mode with bots
- Playable on Internet and LAN
- Compatible with Windows 8/7/Vista




-Autoupdate include
